Dear guests, we are delighted to share that The White Rabbit is welcoming all reservations in anticipation of reopening our doors from 19 June. As we look forward to celebrating your reunion with your loved ones, we invite you to plan ahead with us via reservation link in bio or by calling the restaurant. Guests may expect new exquisite plates of classic European cuisine, delectable desserts on weekdays and relish in sumptuous brunch and elegant tipples on the weekends. We cannot wait to show you how much we have missed you.As we prepare for Hospitality In A Brave New World, we remain committed to our part in protecting everyone in our community and have examined every touchpoint to develop new practices to see the group through the long-term. For more information, you may visit https://lobehold.com/bravenewworld. Meanwhile, The White Rabbit At Home Experience from our takeaway and delivery menu remains available for a romantic meal at home.@lobeholdgroup #thewhiterabbitsg #lobeholdgroup #dempseyhill
